## 9. Conclusion

This reporting period covers the most technically involved phase of Project VoltStream so far. The Silver layer required deliberate engineering decisions around the Non-Operational station filter logic and the deduplication MERGE pattern, both of which directly support the business analysis goals in the Project Charter. The failure-event tracking approach sets up the Gold layer to answer VoltStream's core question: when does extreme weather cause station outages, and which stations are most at risk?

